{
  "text": "In this section, we present and discuss the most related works on spatial clustering in WSNs. A well-reviewed survey of clustering algorithms in WSNs is referred to in [CITATION_1] . As HSC relies on the AR model, we will also briefly review the related work of AR model in WSNs.",
